name: DogSafeStuff

”Alexa, open dog safe stuff”
”Alexa, start dog safe stuff”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dog safe stuff
des:
Ask for certain food names to see if they are safe for dogs. This information has been gathered from various sources online. If ANY source says that the item is bad for dogs, it is listed as bad.

The information here is simply a quick reference and you should ask your pet's veterinarian for definitive answers on whether or not these things are safe for dogs. I can not be held liable for information that was inaccurate when listed on the websites the information was gathered from.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
